    <criterion testable="true">No Dataverse customizations modified in this task (audit only).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">No `.claude/` files modified in this task.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Parallelization: this task is `parallel-group=G` (parallel with tasks 031, 032, 033, 034 which run sequentially among themselves). Specifically, this audit only requires task 030 (scaffold) to be done — the actual Code Page integration isn't a dependency.

    If the dev environment has zero customizations on the standard form (most likely outcome for a relatively new entity like `sprk_communication`), document that explicitly — it de-risks task 038 significantly and lets task 038 proceed without mitigations.

    The audit's HIGH-risk threshold is subjective; a JS handler that BLOCKS save under certain conditions is HIGH-risk; a cosmetic field-visibility rule is LOW-risk.
  </notes>

